l of pear and blackberry compote and dust with icing sugar."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Before frying the brioche, allow to drain for a few seconds.","Fresh or frozen berries may be used.","You can replace the blackberries in this recipe with in-season berries like strawberries or blueberries.","For a 'crème brûlée' finish, dust the cooked pain perdu with caster sugar and caramelise with a kitchen blowtorch."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","40m","4 portions"]}